summary: Explore Tamriel is a project about exploring the lore built around the Elder Scrolls series, this particular mod opens up all of Tamriel to explore using all the lore in the series.
descriptionHtml:
Do not take this as a mod all about exploration and questing, those who pay attention could learn almost all their is to know about Elder Scrolls lore and gain a greater respect for the series.

The following Areas are explorable:
Cyrodiil
Elsweyr
Hammerfell
Summerset Isles
Valenwood
author: Tharp76
